subTitle: Seth, an aspiring sorcerer, sets off on an adventurous journey to battle mysterious creatures called Nemesis, who can vapourise anything just by touching it.

title: Bad Boys II
subTitle: Mike and Marcus, the Miami Police Department detectives, investigate the flow of drugs into Miami. Their search leads them to a dangerous drug lord who is planning to control the city's drug trade.

subTitle: After completing his sentence, a former convict sets out to avenge his brother's murder. As he blazes a trail of violence and vengeance, he is pursued by two police officers and an assassin.

subTitle: An artificial intelligence-enabled fighter-bomber develops sentience when struck by lightning during a mission. Three expert pilots must apprehend the bomber before it precipitates a nuclear war.

title: The Woman King
subTitle: A valiant Agojie general goes through a journey fraught with trauma, unexpected motherhood and a terrifying war against the Oyo to become the &quot;woman king&quot; of Dahomey.

subTitle: Columbus, a college student, joins forces with three eccentric strangers to survive a zombie apocalypse and travel through the south-western USA to a safe haven.

title: The Mitchells vs. the Machines

title: The Equalizer
subTitle: Robert McCall gives up violence and wishes to lead a quiet life. However, brutal events force him to take up the fight for justice once again.

title: The Equalizer 2
subTitle: Robert McCall's close friend, Susan Plummer, is killed while investigating a murder-suicide. As a former marine and spy, he leverages his skills and resources to find the culprit and avenge her death.

title: The Equalizer 3
subTitle: As Robert McCall finds himself forming a new bond with the locals of an Italian town, the region's oppression by the Mafia triggers him to protect his people.

subTitle: Six people from different walks of life participate in an escape room competition to win ten thousand dollars. Things change when they find themselves in horrifying circumstances.
